QuestData.Title: Momentum
QuestData.Description: It looks like we've got more work to do! Having Mr. Noggenfogger ask us to take care of the rest of the pirates is a true honor.$B$BSince you've been SO helpful, why don't you meet me at Lost Rigger Cove? I've just got to slip into something a bit more comfortable, so don't wait on me. I'll beat you there, promise!
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Kelsey Steelspark at Lost Rigger Cove.
QuestData.RewardText: Hi there! The fun's already started!
